org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem

Class BlockStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.poifs.filesystem.BlockStore
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    POIFSFileSystem, POIFSMiniStore 

    public abstract class BlockStore
extends java.lang.Object
    This abstract class describes a way to read, store, chain and free a series of blocks (be they Big or Small ones)(这个抽象类描述了一种读取、存储、链接和释放一系列块（无论是大块还是小块）的方法)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      protected class  BlockStore.ChainLoopDetector
      Used to detect if a chain has a loop in it, so we can bail out with an error rather than spinning away for ever...(用于检测链中是否有循环，这样我们就可以通过错误摆脱，而不是永远旋转.)
